title: Sibling Advicery: Annoying Twinks/Hamilton Tickets
description:
This week on Sibling Advicery Bob and Monét dive into answering your questions about navigating high school drama, diversity in the workplace, situationships, heightism, sex hangups and so much more! 
You can submit your own questions to Bob and Monét by joining their Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/siblingrivalrypodcast
